title: Correction: Open Labware: 3-D Printing Your Own Lab Equipment
fullText:
The names of the 3rd and 4th authors are incorrect and should be: Gregory J. Gage and Timothy C. Marzullo, respectively. Please use the corrected citation below.

‘The NIH 3-D print exchange’ was referenced incorrectly in the text. The correct version is: The NIH 3D Print Exchange. For this reason, Reference 23 is incorrect and should be: National Institutes of Health (2015) The NIH 3D Print Exchange. http://3dprint.nih.gov/.
